# ==============================================================================
# C / C++ / CMake / Visual Studio / Multi-Project Monorepo通用全局 .gitignore
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. 通用构建与输出目录 (针对所有子项目递归生效)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
**/build/
**/Build/
**/BUILD/
**/out/
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/Debug/
**/Release/
**/x64/
**/x86/
**/ARM/
**/ARM64/

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. 编译生成的最终二进制程序与库文件
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.a
*.lib
*.out
*.app
*.gch
*.pch

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. 编译中间目标文件与调试符号 (MSVC / GCC / Clang)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.o
*.obj
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.idb
*.exp
*.map
*.ipb
*.iobj
*.tlog/
*.lastbuildstate
*.unsuccessfulbuild

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. CMake / Ninja / Make 构建系统自动生成文件
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CMakeScripts/
cmake_install.cmake
CTestTestfile.cmake
_deps/
*.cmake
!CMakeLists.txt
*.ninja
.ninja_deps
.ninja_log

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. 微软 Visual Studio 专属临时与生成工程文件
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.sln.docstates
*.ncb
*.sdf
*.opensdf
*.db
*.ipch

# 注：如果你采用纯 CMake 驱动，生成的 Visual Studio 解决方案本身也无需进入 Git
*.sln
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.filters
*.vcxproj.user

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. 旧式 Eclipse / CodeBlocks / Qt / 其他工作区配置文件
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.cproject
.project
.settings/
*.layout
*.depend

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 7. 操作系统与编辑器本地临时缓存
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
*.bak
*.tmp
